{"tid":475841,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"自動波真係無用","createTime":"2017-11-21T13:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T08:54:34.000Z","uid":87155,"like":8,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2281323de192f48669f5d8cfb88da852009d30e4","tid":475841,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"一黎 去旅行 自駕遊無你份<br />\n二黎 香港少數人 係自動波 十個有九個都棍<br />\n三黎 雖然話就話棍波搵食用 但好多車你自動波都無份<br />\n<br />\n四黎 比人知你自動波牌 實恥笑你話知你咩車<br />\n<br />\n其他 等你地後補"},{"pid":"195fc87e5d94530863595d130a0afb198de86925","tid":475841,"uid":74262,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96a846072066e96bbdedbe15ea43ace1fab5e732","tid":475841,"uid":42072,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一黎 去旅行 自駕遊無你份<br />\n二黎 香港少數人 係自動波 十個有九個都棍<br />\n三黎 雖然話就話棍波搵食用 但好多車你自動波都無份<br />\n<br />\n四黎 比人知你自動波牌 實恥笑你話知你咩車<br />\n<br />\n其他 等你地後補</blockquote><br />\n岩岩考完牌就係到打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咪一鳩樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 油塘棍仔一tick<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75e35a548304fe7e7c2563d70126c3d53e4aa5d","tid":475841,"uid":87155,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:23:19.000Z","msg":"屌 唔記得利申自己 <br />\n自動波垃圾牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aa8c1a48d1f15a4abe7b23db8d5ec56a0f983d","tid":475841,"uid":89801,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"老老實實 上連登笑人地自動波既人 考左棍波車牌之後揸過幾多次棍波車?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 日日揸棍波車"},{"pid":"592c8878377f78ec1ad478bad6d03fb3bec0f810","tid":475841,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"最垃圾係 無得自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158c7cb94a3e9a4f9cec7e3ae70b904931447427","tid":475841,"uid":9115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最垃圾係 無得自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實而家自駕遊,多數唔租棍波俾遊客<br />\n一黎唔知租果個駕駛經驗,有棍牌唔代表熟棍<br />\n二黎遊客通常唔熟當地交通規例<br />\n係呢種情況,仲要遊客用棍波,意外率太高"},{"pid":"ca8ab56a515b659e65e0616133ba6fe18ded0bdb","tid":475841,"uid":19867,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實 上連登笑人地自動波既人 考左棍波車牌之後揸過幾多次棍波車?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 日日揸棍波車</blockquote><br />\n學自動波其實冇問題<br />\n但唔好識少人一樣野 仲要話學棍波既人ON9"},{"pid":"63203084e8dda973a018e79c7bb8e176236b85f1","tid":475841,"uid":87155,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老實實 上連登笑人地自動波既人 考左棍波車牌之後揸過幾多次棍波車?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 日日揸棍波車</blockquote><br />\n學自動波其實冇問題<br />\n但唔好識少人一樣野 仲要話學棍波既人ON9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 我自動波牌真心唔敢同人講識<br />\n<br />\n大家自動牌慳d洗唔好再撩事鬥非了"},{"pid":"4aa10c756f6dca1be670187b0edd1b8d6e3c1499","tid":475841,"uid":98474,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"揸到識唔用clutch都轉到波先講自己識揸棍波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考個爛鬼12牌都好似好勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfa53dd07eb91699304ad2977c8df04e3e03ed8","