41,"uid":134945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個話自動波冇得自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想問 我去親旅行自駕遊租車都租自動波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無去過南法自駕遊？<br />\n成個場百架車得3架AT，我想租1500cc佢話AT得X5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去歐洲基本上揸棍<br />\n美日澳就自動"},{"pid":"bf5fab0fbf0c183eebd382e3ce29d5496729e979","tid":475841,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最垃圾係 無得自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實而家自駕遊,多數唔租棍波俾遊客<br />\n一黎唔知租果個駕駛經驗,有棍牌唔代表熟棍<br />\n二黎遊客通常唔熟當地交通規例<br />\n係呢種情況,仲要遊客用棍波,意外率太高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我每年返英國租車都係楂棍波...<br />\n一樣係拎香港牌去租都無問題"}]}